title: E-TextEditor 2.01 with RegFix
description:
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

I was just going to upload the regfile that I made but since this seems to have disappeared from TPB and the site is going to a japanese site I am uploading the software as well, enjoy. This is a nice editor that I use sometimes and deserves a torrent.

Why I made the regfix and decided to post it here is that the crack was only useful for 30 days, then the software stopped running, so when that happens run the regfix file and you will get 30 days again, just do that every 30 days and voila.

Original Site Link (That Used to Be): http://www.e-texteditor.com/
Github Link: https://github.com/etexteditor/e
